Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Other Hardware
Inrad Optics, Inc. develops, manufactures, and supplies products for photonics industry sectors.  The Company's product areas include crystals and crystal components, custom optics, systems and instruments, and thin film services. Inrad's customers include corporations, defense industries, the United States Government, and researchers at laboratories and universities.




