			Company Description 


			Inrad Optics, Inc. develops, manufactures and markets products and services for use in photonics industry sectors. It manufactures crystal-based optical components and devices, custom optical components from both glass and metal, and precision optical and opto-mechanical assemblies. The company's pr...
		


                Inrad Optics, Inc. develops, manufactures and markets products and services for use in photonics industry sectors. It manufactures crystal-based optical components and devices, custom optical components from both glass and metal, and precision optical and opto-mechanical assemblies. The company's products include optical components and laser system devices and instrumentation. Inrad Optics was founded in April 1973 and is headquartered in Northvale, NJ.
            




